Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Lame duck President Reagan, 1988
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yds3x
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 20 May 1988
Considered a lame duck since his farewell State of the Union address in January 1988, Cooke muses on the real power of outgoing President Reagan.